<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Diligent efforts ... including =E2=
=80=9Ccountless hours negotiating with one of the largest insurance compani=
es in the world,=E2=80=9D have proven that =E2=80=9Cobtaining an appeal bon=
d in the full amount=E2=80=9D of the Judgment =E2=80=9Cis not possible unde=
