idth: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: none !importa=
nt; background-color: transparent !important; display: inline-block;">
<span>[8]</span>
</a>=C2=A0They want the deal. But in the past, DWAC has <a href=3D"https://=
link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34741977.257361/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb=
21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMDktMDYvdHJ1bXAtc3BhYy1kb2Vzbi10=
LWhhdmUtdGhlLXZvdGVzP2NtcGlkPUJCRDAzMTkyNF9NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1=
haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTI0MDMxOSZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249bW=
9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB5c3c686f" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" item=
scope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decorat=
ion: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #00000=
0; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">failed to get share=
holder approval</a> for obviously good things because its heavily retail sh=
areholder base doesn=E2=80=99t vote that much. I would be surprised if that=
 happened on the merger vote, but it=E2=80=99s not impossible.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Then, the deal has to close right after the vo=
te. At that point, Trump will personally have=C2=A0shares worth about $2.8 =
billion.<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-9" style=3D"color: #0=
00000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-b=
ottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: none !important; background-colo=
r: transparent !important; display: inline-block;">
<span>[9]</span>
</a></p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Also, Trump=E2=80=99s shares are subject to a =
lockup agreement, so he=E2=80=99s <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbus=
iness.com/click/34741977.257361/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9BcmNoaXZlcy9lZGd=
hci9kYXRhLzE4NDk2MzUvMDAwMTE5MzEyNTI0MDM4NTkwL2Q0MDg1NjNkNDI0YjQuaHRtI3JvbT=
