border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style=
: solid; background-color: #ccc;">accounting</a> <a href=3D"https://link.ma=
il.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34741977.257361/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuaGtpY3BhLm9y=
